11#import "RTCDefaultVideoEncoderFactory.h"
12
13#import "RTCH264ProfileLevelId.h"
14#import "RTCVideoEncoderH264.h"
15#import "api/video_codec/RTCVideoCodecConstants.h"
16#import "api/video_codec/RTCVideoEncoderVP8.h"
17#import "base/RTCVideoCodecInfo.h"
18#if defined(RTC_ENABLE_VP9)
19#import "api/video_codec/RTCVideoEncoderVP9.h"
20#endif
21#if !defined(DISABLE_H265)
22#import "RTCH265ProfileLevelId.h"
23#import "RTCVideoEncoderH265.h"
24#endif
25
26@implementation RTCDefaultVideoEncoderFactory {
27 bool _supportsH265;
28 bool _supportsVP9Profile0;
29 bool _supportsVP9Profile2;
30 bool _useLowLatencyH264;
31}
32
33- (id)initWithH265:(bool)supportsH265 vp9Profile0:(bool)supportsVP9Profile0 vp9Profile2:(bool)supportsVP9Profile2 lowLatencyH264:(bool)useLowLatencyH264
34{
35 self = [super init];
36 if (self) {
37 _supportsH265 = supportsH265;
38 _supportsVP9Profile0 = supportsVP9Profile0;
39 _supportsVP9Profile2 = supportsVP9Profile2;
40 _useLowLatencyH264 = useLowLatencyH264;
41 }
42 return self;
43}
44
45+ (NSArray<RTCVideoCodecInfo *> *)supportedCodecs {
46 return [self supportedCodecsWithH265:true vp9Profile0:true vp9Profile2:true];
47}
48
49+ (NSArray<RTCVideoCodecInfo *> *)supportedCodecsWithH265:(bool)supportsH265 vp9Profile0:(bool)supportsVP9Profile0 vp9Profile2:(bool)supportsVP9Profile2 {
50
51 NSMutableArray<RTCVideoCodecInfo *> *codecs = [[NSMutableArray alloc] initWithCapacity:8];
52
53 [codecs addObject: [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecH264Name parameters: @{
54 @"profile-level-id" : kRTCMaxSupportedH264ProfileLevelConstrainedHigh,
55 @"level-asymmetry-allowed" : @"1",
56 @"packetization-mode" : @"1",
57 }]];
58 [codecs addObject: [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecH264Name parameters: @{
59 @"profile-level-id" : kRTCMaxSupportedH264ProfileLevelConstrainedBaseline,
60 @"level-asymmetry-allowed" : @"1",
61 @"packetization-mode" : @"1",
62 }]];
63 [codecs addObject: [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecH264Name parameters: @{
64 @"profile-level-id" : kRTCMaxSupportedH264ProfileLevelConstrainedHigh,
65 @"level-asymmetry-allowed" : @"1",
66 @"packetization-mode" : @"0",
67 }]];
68 [codecs addObject: [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecH264Name parameters: @{
69 @"profile-level-id" : kRTCMaxSupportedH264ProfileLevelConstrainedBaseline,
70 @"level-asymmetry-allowed" : @"1",
71 @"packetization-mode" : @"0",
72 }]];
73
74#if !defined(RTC_DISABLE_H265)
75 if (supportsH265) {
76 RTCVideoCodecInfo *h265Info = [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecH265Name];
77 [codecs addObject:h265Info];
78 }
79#endif
80
81 RTCVideoCodecInfo *vp8Info = [[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecVp8Name];
82 [codecs addObject:vp8Info];
83
84#if defined(RTC_ENABLE_VP9)
85 if (supportsVP9Profile0) {
86 [codecs addObject:[[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecVp9Name parameters: @{
87 @"profile-id" : @"0",
88 }]];
89 }
90 if (supportsVP9Profile2) {
91 [codecs addObject:[[RTCVideoCodecInfo alloc] initWithName:kRTCVideoCodecVp9Name parameters: @{
92 @"profile-id" : @"2",
93 }]];
94 }
95#endif
96
97 return codecs;
98}
99
100- (id<RTCVideoEncoder>)createEncoder:(RTCVideoCodecInfo *)info {
101 if ([info.name isEqualToString:kRTCVideoCodecH264Name]) {
102 RTCVideoEncoderH264* encoder = [[RTCVideoEncoderH264 alloc] initWithCodecInfo:info];
103 [encoder setH264LowLatencyEncoderEnabled:_useLowLatencyH264];
104 return encoder;
105 } else if ([info.name isEqualToString:kRTCVideoCodecVp8Name]) {
106 return [RTCVideoEncoderVP8 vp8Encoder];
107#if defined(RTC_ENABLE_VP9)
108 } else if ([info.name isEqualToString:kRTCVideoCodecVp9Name]) {
109 return [RTCVideoEncoderVP9 vp9Encoder:info];
110#endif
111#if !defined(DISABLE_H265)
112 } else if (@available(iOS 11, *)) {
113 if ([info.name isEqualToString:kRTCVideoCodecH265Name]) {
114 return [[RTCVideoEncoderH265 alloc] initWithCodecInfo:info];
115 }
116#endif
117 }
118
119 return nil;
120}
121
122- (NSArray<RTCVideoCodecInfo *> *)supportedCodecs {
123 return [[self class] supportedCodecsWithH265:_supportsH265 vp9Profile0:_supportsVP9Profile0 vp9Profile2: _supportsVP9Profile2];
124}
125
126@end
